item.title: CVE-2023-0421|2023-05-08T13:58:04.382Z -- unknown -- cloud%20manager
item.description: The Cloud Manager WordPress plugin through 1.0 does not sanitise and escape the query param ricerca before outputting it in an admin panel, allowing unauthenticated attackers to trick a logged in admin to trigger a XSS payload by clicking a link.
